1 A BILL for an Act to create and enact a new section to chapter 54-17 of the North Dakota
2 Century Code, relating to a research technology park grant program; to provide an
3 appropriation; and to provide a report.
4 BE IT ENACTED BY THE LEGISLATIVE ASSEMBLY OF NORTH DAKOTA:
5 SECTION 1. A new section to chapter 54-17 of the North Dakota Century Code is created
6 and enacted as follows:
7 Research technology park grant program - North Dakota state university - Report .
8 1. The industrial commission shall administer the research technology park gran t
9 program. Subject to legislative appropriations, the industrial commission shal l
10 distribute grant funding to the research technology park at North Dakota state
11 university. The research technology park shall use the funds in accordance with this
12 section.
13 2. The research technology park at North Dakota state university is created to conduct
14 exploratory, transformational, and innovative research and product development
15 activities that advance intelligent autonomous mobile equipment opportunities and
16 benefit the state's economy and environment through:
17 a. Exploratory research and development of technologies and methodologies that
18 facilitate the prudent development and efficient use of the state's autonomous
19 agriculture resources and defense capabilities;
20 b. Access to advanced robotics and artificial intelligence expertise for timely
21 scientific and engineering activities to support the state's interests; and
